{"word":"τυννοῦτος","slug":"τυννοῦτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>τυννοῦτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:lengthened'>lengthd.</a> form of <a href='S:τυννός'><el>τυννός</el></a>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a>\n<p/><i>tantillus</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; with <el>ι</el> demonstr., <el>τυννουτοσί, -ονί</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> and <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> <el>τυννουτουί, -ῳί</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/>"}]}